The first issue we will tackle is the one reporting the use of Weblogic ApplicationLifecyleEvent and Weblogic LifecycleListener in this file. Edit the file to make these changes:
package com.redhat.coolstore.utils;

import javax.annotation.PostConstruct;
import javax.annotation.PreDestroy;
import javax.ejb.Startup;
